Package src.model

Class Report

java.lang.Object
src.model.Report
public class Report extends Object
Represents a summary report entry for a booking and payment. Includes key information about the applicant, flat, and transaction status.

      Constructs a new report entry summarizing a flat booking.
      Parameters:
      applicantName - Name of the applicant.
      applicantNRIC - NRIC of the applicant.
      age - Age of the applicant.
      maritalStatus - Marital status of the applicant.
      projectName - Name of the project booked.
      flatTypeBooked - Type of flat booked (e.g., 2-Room).
      flatPrice - Price of the booked flat.
      bookingStatus - Booking status (e.g., BOOKED).
      paymentStatus - Payment status (e.g., PROCESSED).
      bookingDate - Date the booking was made (nullable).
      receiptId - Receipt ID issued after payment (nullable).
